c: 58
v: 3
t: "Baye bazali koloba na basi na bango été bazali lokola mokongo ya bamama na bango, sima bazongeli (bango) тре basaleli oyo balobaki te, esengeli na bango kokangola mowumbu moko yambo ete basangana na bango. Wana ezali тропа kolendisa bino, тре Allah azali na sango ya maye bozali kosala"